. Sales dropped to $6.61 billion, a 0.68% decrease between quarters. In Q1, Broadcom brought in $6.66 billion in sales but only earned $1.84 billion. ", "symbols": ["AVGO"], "updated_at": "2021-06-28T14:32:03Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/21/06/21745351/return-on-capital-employed-overview-broadcom"}]